  <h1>Les monades en Haskell, expliquées sans le jargon</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>Par Coldwast</span><span>Mis à jour le 14 juin 2026</span><span>8 min de lecture</span><span class="tag">#haskell</span><span class="tag">#monads</span><span class="tag">#concepts</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1613068687893-5e85b4638b56?w=1200&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Du code source sur un écran sombre" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
